So I haven't updated this since...April of 2005. I was just browsing the internet this morning and I started reading some of my older entries. I must say, they are pretty stupid, but how intelligent can a person be at 14 right? 
My life hasnt gotten much more exciting since then. Although, NEVER AGAIN will I finish one of these entries with "i love svs".

That is completely juvenille and ridiculous and everyone knows I love Jordan :) so no need for me to be talking about my secret little crushes anymore.

I'll probably be using this more often now since I haven't got anything better to do with my time.

I'm working at a Subway, for now. I'm pretty sure I'll be fired soon:(

Im graduating in a few months so I'm just trying really hard to get work done and all that stuff that requires motivation, something I lack horribly.

I also failed my drivers test so I'm still a loser without my license :) Ill go to take my test again on May 24th. Wish me luck!

Well, since myspace has taken over the world, and my pathetic life, I'm going to log in to that now :)

This week (which has been hell for me) has proven that no matter how much homework or reading you hafto do, and no matter how early you hafto get up, there are still ONLY 24 hours in a day to get done what needs to be done. So if you dont get your stuff together, well thats just too damn bad because life isnt exactly notorious for giving people breaks.

anyways...yeah im reading this book about stephen king, and its like reading jibberish or something. its SO BORING. All I want to read right now is the Godfather Returns..(i am number 13 on the waiting list for that :o)
anyways...all I did yesterday was BIOLOGY. I never want to pick up that book again. I never want to read about that again. I just want my Godfather book. GOSH!

its 11:38 and i just woke up alittle while ago. now there is something wrong with that. If only I had gotten up at say...8? Then maybe I could have this book (along with the rest of my schoolwork) done at a decent hour. Maybe THEN i would be able to go to sleep sometime before 2:30 a.m.
its so hard being me :)

Im hungry and I want some eggs :)

leave some comments GOSH
